content: Tried to download app, said it was designed for an older android and to check for an update. Screen size was incorrect and could not navigate around the app.
Do not trust the offset calculation. Always double check the math which really means you have to layout anyway.
It would be 5 stars if the bottom information wasn't cut off of the screen. I can see half of the words "offset length" and the corresponding number but nothing below that
Has worked for me every time. Wish though for a update for newer phones
I love this app but it doesn't fit on the screen anymore. The bottom tabs are covered. Can we get a round to oval converter?

Works great except for the bottom task bars to switch between round & rectangular duct are cut off a bit. I've used it for years on iPhone, works like a charm every time if you punch in the correct numbers
Real handy app  saves time
This app is just plain awesome!
Doesn't work on 2017 phone
Line items pushed together. Can't read them to put dimensions in.
Only gave 1/2 the screen.. no place to input. Only round duct no other applications like the ad shows.
Can't see the full screen on my galexy s6 active
Bottom buttons for "round" "rectangular" and "tools" are cut off, but usable. Back to 5 stars when fixed... Galaxy S6
I am a sheet metal worker with over 18 years in the field. Other than the bottom task bar being cut off slightly, this app saves me a ton of time. I'm recommending it to all my coworkers.

If you know how to do offsets using a calculator this will be a breeze! It's also very useful for teaching people how to figure offsets as well. I've checked this many times and it's always been right. So now I use it to double check my work. Very simple, accurate, and saves time! The one thing I can think of to make it even better is a square offset calculator using two different size elbows and your cut piece being a transition. You can do it using this app but it takes more time than the usual offsets...
Great great app. Bottom line. I love it!
Had a problem with Android. Market saying it was incompatible with my bionic,  the developer fixed it promptly and now I am enjoying this great must have app.
The best tool for field measuring! It makes it super easy and it's always right!
Would rate it higher if I could read all the options. Half the words are cut off in some of the option. Would rate 5 if this was fixed
Best application ever for a sheet metal installer.

I like the app but its hard to see all of  the buttons some are cut off I'm not sure if it's the  programming on a new up to date phone. I tried removeing the app and reinstalling the app but that didnt work.. could be 5 stars if you corrected that issue..
It looks like it would save time... If it worked with out crashing...  Fix this and it might be worth something.
Best app for sheet metal workers!
Total waste of my time. Misleading bigtime!
Saved loads of time, allowed me to get much more done.
Worth every penny!  EVO 4g
Very easy to use. It will save valuable time.
